---
title: Aubergine Tagliatelle with Chilli and Sun-Dried Tomatoes
description: Sun-dried tomatoes really do bring a taste of sunshine to any dish you add them to. Their flavour
is intense so a little goes a long way. Here they combine with grilled aubergine and whole wheat
tagliatelle for a plateful of rustic, summery charm. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/aubergine-tagliatelle-week-f5c9ef32.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/aubergine-tagliatelle-week-d2e39ef8.pdf
